<p>The renovations are finished! This generator is purely JavaScript. <b>Known issues:</b><br>
- Certain verbs can take improper direct objects (for example, <i>yongasabido hantasa</i>)<br>
If you encounter issues, please let me know @identityarchitect on Tumblr or on the Adamantine's Drainbox thread of the <a href="https://yongasabi.freeforums.net/">Yongasabi Forums</a>.
</p>

